  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/16a9e1ad1c0e6da0fbee27dfd2b7df1b.webp?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/18056f165ade6e43edafa7a627f33255.poster.avif?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/18056f165ade6e43edafa7a627f33255.webm?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/18056f165ade6e43edafa7a627f33255.mp4?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired from the famous mod from Counter Strike, surf on all kinds of ramps ! <strong>Intuitive tutorials</strong> will help you learn and master this <strong>unique mechanic</strong> and <strong>cool audio design</strong> makes it even more fun ! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/ee9db390ed659ee29bb0547c3b4d3799.webp?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/c47734df2071c338f4643b92c069e17e.poster.avif?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/c47734df2071c338f4643b92c069e17e.webm?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/c47734df2071c338f4643b92c069e17e.mp4?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jump</strong>, <strong>double jump</strong>, and <strong>even bunny hops</strong> if you have enough speed ! Use them all and chose wisely your timing to <strong>keep your flow</strong> ! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/4bed31b152c619017360c08886ec8a1a.webp?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/0717a4edd0256e4047593456e14b60e2.poster.avif?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/0717a4edd0256e4047593456e14b60e2.webm?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/0717a4edd0256e4047593456e14b60e2.mp4?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take the time to enjoy beautiful watercolor textures and a <strong>mysterious atmosphere</strong> alongside a peaceful <strong>35 minutes long soundtrack</strong>. Don't forget to explore the world to <strong>uncover secrets</strong>... be careful though, some might try to escape ! <strong>Hidden characters</strong> might reveal a thing or two about the world you live in as well...<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/ce0b7f6068da23352739a3913fb53517.webp?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/1d1f2280a514bcbb3dc7b4b970121e3d.poster.avif?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/1d1f2280a514bcbb3dc7b4b970121e3d.webm?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/1d1f2280a514bcbb3dc7b4b970121e3d.mp4?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beat quickly the <strong>30+ handcrafted levels</strong> to earn medals from <strong>Bronze to Gold</strong>... or even <strong>try to beat my time</strong> if you have what it takes ! Compare your times with your friends on <strong>leaderboards </strong>as well !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I am a <strong>solo dev </strong>that have been making games with passion for years, I hope you will enjoy Hoverflow, <strong>my first big project</strong> 🖤 Join the Discord if you have any question, I usually answer pretty quickly !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simon.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/16a9e1ad1c0e6da0fbee27dfd2b7df1b.webp?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/18056f165ade6e43edafa7a627f33255.poster.avif?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/18056f165ade6e43edafa7a627f33255.webm?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/18056f165ade6e43edafa7a627f33255.mp4?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired from the famous mod from Counter Strike, surf on all kinds of ramps ! <strong>Intuitive tutorials</strong> will help you learn and master this <strong>unique mechanic</strong> and <strong>cool audio design</strong> makes it even more fun ! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/ee9db390ed659ee29bb0547c3b4d3799.webp?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/c47734df2071c338f4643b92c069e17e.poster.avif?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/c47734df2071c338f4643b92c069e17e.webm?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/c47734df2071c338f4643b92c069e17e.mp4?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jump</strong>, <strong>double jump</strong>, and <strong>even bunny hops</strong> if you have enough speed ! Use them all and chose wisely your timing to <strong>keep your flow</strong> ! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/4bed31b152c619017360c08886ec8a1a.webp?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/0717a4edd0256e4047593456e14b60e2.poster.avif?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/0717a4edd0256e4047593456e14b60e2.webm?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/0717a4edd0256e4047593456e14b60e2.mp4?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take the time to enjoy beautiful watercolor textures and a <strong>mysterious atmosphere</strong> alongside a peaceful <strong>35 minutes long soundtrack</strong>. Don't forget to explore the world to <strong>uncover secrets</strong>... be careful though, some might try to escape ! <strong>Hidden characters</strong> might reveal a thing or two about the world you live in as well...<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/ce0b7f6068da23352739a3913fb53517.webp?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/1d1f2280a514bcbb3dc7b4b970121e3d.poster.avif?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/1d1f2280a514bcbb3dc7b4b970121e3d.webm?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/1d1f2280a514bcbb3dc7b4b970121e3d.mp4?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beat quickly the <strong>30+ handcrafted levels</strong> to earn medals from <strong>Bronze to Gold</strong>... or even <strong>try to beat my time</strong> if you have what it takes ! Compare your times with your friends on <strong>leaderboards </strong>as well !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I am a <strong>solo dev </strong>that have been making games with passion for years, I hope you will enjoy Hoverflow, <strong>my first big project</strong> 🖤 Join the Discord if you have any question, I usually answer pretty quickly !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simon.</p>",
